show.description: Tasha was betrayed by her husband, forced to get a divorce, and leave the family. in multiple debts, she started to fight for her daughter's custody, as her ex-husband plans to sabotage her with his new wife. but when Tasha got help from an unknown handsome cab driver, her whole life changed.
